# Styling Standards

## SCSS Module Structure
- **File naming**: Use `.module.scss` for component styles
- **Class naming**: Use camelCase for class names
- **Component prefix**: Prefix classes with component name

## SCSS File Structure
```scss
// ComponentName.module.scss
.componentName {
  // Base styles
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  
  // State styles
  &:hover {
    // Hover effects
  }
  
  &:focus {
    // Focus styles
  }
  
  &:disabled {
    // Disabled state
    opacity: 0.6;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }
  
  // Variant styles
  &[data-variant="primary"] {
    background-color: var(--primary-color);
  }
  
  &[data-variant="secondary"] {
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
  }
  
  // Size styles
  &[data-size="small"] {
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }
  
  &[data-size="large"] {
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
  
  // Responsive styles
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    // Mobile-specific styles
  }
}
```

## CSS Variables
Use CSS variables for consistent theming:
```scss
:root {
  // Colors
  --primary-color: #007bff;
  --secondary-color: #6c757d;
  --success-color: #28a745;
  --danger-color: #dc3545;
  --warning-color: #ffc107;
  --info-color: #17a2b8;
  
  // Typography
  --font-family-base: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
  --font-size-base: 1rem;
  --line-height-base: 1.5;
  
  // Spacing
  --spacing-xs: 0.25rem;
  --spacing-sm: 0.5rem;
  --spacing-md: 1rem;
  --spacing-lg: 1.5rem;
  --spacing-xl: 3rem;
  
  // Border radius
  --border-radius: 0.375rem;
  --border-radius-lg: 0.5rem;
  --border-radius-sm: 0.25rem;
  
  // Shadows
  --shadow-sm: 0 0.125rem 0.25rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075);
  --shadow: 0 0.5rem 1rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  --shadow-lg: 0 1rem 3rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.175);
}
```

## Responsive Design
- **Mobile-first**: Start with mobile styles, then add desktop
- **Breakpoints**: Use Bootstrap breakpoints
  - `xs`: 0px and up
  - `sm`: 576px and up
  - `md`: 768px and up
  - `lg`: 992px and up
  - `xl`: 1200px and up
  - `xxl`: 1400px and up

## Bootstrap Integration
- **Utility classes**: Use Bootstrap utility classes when possible
- **Custom components**: Extend Bootstrap components with custom styles
- **Grid system**: Use Bootstrap grid for layouts
- **Components**: Leverage React Bootstrap components

## Accessibility
- **Color contrast**: Ensure sufficient contrast ratios
- **Focus indicators**: Clear focus states for keyboard navigation
- **Reduced motion**: Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` media query
- **High contrast**: Support high contrast mode

## Performance
- **CSS-in-JS**: Avoid runtime CSS-in-JS for better performance
- **Critical CSS**: Inline critical styles for above-the-fold content
- **Unused CSS**: Remove unused styles to reduce bundle size
- **CSS modules**: Use for component-scoped styles
